<p>{{#note_ref 1}}{{/note_ref}} I use data uris in my stylesheets for the patterned backgrounds you see on the banners and body. This is another example of giving a progressive enhanced aesthetic experience to those using modern browsers, and falling back to a plain background colour if data uris are not supported - which I believe is IE7 and lower&hellip;now we're getting ancient!</p>

